<Content>
  <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4">Specimen Digitization</h3>
  <p>
    This project is led by Dr. Nurainas at the Herbarium Universitas Andalas
    (ANDA) funded through the collection and data mobilization grant provided by
    the Global Biodiversity Information Facility (GBIF). We aim to digitize
    >65,000 sheets of the herbarium specimens at ANDA and make the data
    accessible through the GBIF portal.
  </p>
  <div class="mt-4 mb-2 text-semibold">Published datasets:</div>
  <ProjectPubs author="Nurainas et. al.">
    <PubButton
      author="Nurainas N, Amolia R R, Taufiq A, Handika H, Syamsuardi S"
      year="2024a"
      title="Flora of Sumatra : Vascular plant collection from Batang Toru Forest deposited in ANDA Herbarium"
      doi="https://doi.org/10.15468/ue7xyn"
    />
    <span class={spaceClasses}>,</span>
    <PubButton
      author="Nurainas N, Taufiq A, Handika H, Syamsuardi S"
      year="2024b"
      title="Flora of Sumatra: Vascular plant collection of selected families deposited at Herbarium of Andalas University (ANDA)"
      doi="https://doi.org/10.15468/sncpxn"
    />
    <span class={spaceClasses}>,</span>
    <PubButton
      author="Nurainas N, Taufiq A, Handika H, Harapan T S, Syamsuardi S"
      year="2024c"
      title="Flora Sumatra: Digitizing and data basing specimens of the Sumatran Flora deposited at Herbarium Universitas Andalas (ANDA)-Part 2"
      doi="https://doi.org/10.15468/55evew "
    />
