</Content>
<Content>
  <h3 class="font-semibold mt-4">
    Genomics and Systematics of Antbirds in the Neotropics
  </h3>
  <p>
    I mentored to students: Marky Mutchler (the University of Chicago) and Ryan
    Zucker (Cornell University). Both of them are under the supervision of <Link
      text="Dr. Glaucia Del-Rio"
      url="https://www.gdel-rio.com/"
    />, the University of Florida. We aim to understand the genomic basis of
    speciation and systematics of antbirds in the Neotropics. My involement is
    primarily in the phylogenomic analyses of the studies.
  </p>
</Content>
